# Definir ruta per defecte adaptador de xarxa

Fitxer: /etc/network/interfaces.d/route-config 

```bash
echo "
auto enp1s0
iface enp1s0 inet static
    address 172.20.1.1
    netmask 255.255.0.0
    post-up ip route add 172.20.0.0/16 dev enp1s0 " > /etc/network/interfaces.d/route-config 
```

```bash
ip r show
```

Sortida
```
default via 192.168.120.1 dev enp2s0 proto dhcp src 192.168.121.84 metric 100 
172.20.0.0/16 dev enp1s0 proto kernel scope link src 172.20.1.1 
192.168.120.0/22 dev enp2s0 proto kernel scope link src 192.168.121.84 metric 100 
```
